Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.87,0:24:24.15,中文歌词,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}漫漫长路上踽踽独行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.15,0:24:31.81,中文歌词,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}蓦然回首众人在远方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.11,0:24:39.39,中文歌词,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}纵使如此我仍不止步
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.39,0:24:45.32,中文歌词,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}因这是我唯一的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.84,0:24:53.10,中文歌词,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}内心已经无一丝恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.48,0:25:01.54,中文歌词,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我这样轻声勉励自己
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.97,0:25:12.61,中文歌词,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}人总有天会面对孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.61,0:25:20.37,中文歌词,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}故人只留在回忆之中
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.37,0:25:28.07,中文歌词,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}为了到时能笑看孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.07,0:25:35.40,中文歌词,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我愿战斗到最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.40,0:25:44.61,中文歌词,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}绝对不流落一滴眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------ed end-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说她一下子和大量的意识同化了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.18,0:01:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 优莉作为领袖已经做得很完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回避了战线最大的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 谁也没有料想到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工会里面会有大量的分身在埋伏我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:01:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上 那个是奏的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.59,0:02:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是冷酷的奏所计划的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟也算是奏 这也是没法子的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么说我心里倒好受些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 「没有医院什么的 因为没人会生病」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你说的么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么不醒过来啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Beats！ 第九章 In Your Memory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是迄今为止未曾有过的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见到那种状态的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.99,0:02:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据某些情况 或许有可能永远不会醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才正是异常事态 她会醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:03:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟早会醒过来 只不过是睡久了些而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的她会是哪个人格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 椎名说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说明这是相当重要的问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 是哪个天使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是原来的天使吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们一起钓鱼的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那些攻击我们的人格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是冷酷且好战的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,论数量可是至少一百比一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在失去意识的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是那些大量的人格在她的小脑袋里…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样乱作一团互相排斥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 万一醒过来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人格也会是一百那方的么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照比例来讲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按原来的人格醒来的概率约为1%
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经在采取措施了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经派遣竹山侵入天使区域
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且随同能够解读说明书的队友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TK和松下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责看守他俩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看TK那样 英语却完全不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,删除所有数据
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更改登陆密码
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屏蔽全部的技能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这只拖得了一时 你明白么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使迟早会克服这些障碍 然后再次输入数据
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把电脑毁掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电脑拿电脑室的备用品来代替 要多少就有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,软件也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 今天大家的脑子都好好噢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道吃了脑残灵么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外就听天由命了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神会眷顾那一方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 过点了 入学考试
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点晕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,额头上流血了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:05:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意识怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:05:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉呢 想吐么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你是医生么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 我只是个学生而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站得起来么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来扶你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真惨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 先找救援
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去救助其他里面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要紧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还有点晕 我叫五十岚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫音无
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能不能获救
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找出口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能出去 我就会去呼叫救援
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话我一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电筒我借用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绝对会获救的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:07:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:08:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当困难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隧道前后都被沙石堵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机也没信号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法和外部联系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后我们要同舟共济
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要抱着自私自利的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把食物和饮用水集中起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平等的进行分配
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候变成你指挥了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那谁来指挥？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来负责照顾伤员？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他懂医疗知识
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.13,0:09:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会想不管伤员生死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒…倒不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对会有人来救我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要忍耐到那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起坚持下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口渴的人跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食品会定时分配
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不舒服的人就叫音无
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再忍耐一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事就叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有自制便当和点心一些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝的有瓶装茶和饮用水五六瓶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约能坚持三天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么富有献身精神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你打算投身红十字会出国从事医疗救援么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 倒没有那种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要当真
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你要保存体力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然会第一个倒下的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你丫的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙抢了水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水被……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了老大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把我绑起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你便
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正谁也不会得救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 你们都清楚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那回事 我们会得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说漂亮话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚他把珍贵的饮用水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个是我那一份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后我都不会喝水了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你们放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来打他一顿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我不解气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我们会好好教训他一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把我的分给你喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 把这家伙带到别处去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无 音无
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点不妙 你过来看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活过来!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从那天起为了什么而付出努力？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…初音使我得知了自己的生存意义
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是又眼睁睁地看着别人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有任何改变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是仍然那样无能为力么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是比起那时毫无改变么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先休息一下比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想再看会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 要是着凉就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.34,0:13:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么总不见好转呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有捐献者就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:13:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捐献者？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十岚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有笔没
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行有疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:34.12,注释,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（大意为同意死后捐献所框选的器官）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真服了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样先处理好后事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算万一自己死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个身体还能为他人所用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让自己不枉白活一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你真是非常了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么绝望的他们都把希望寄托在别人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你挽救了这里所有人的人生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 音无
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听见没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏 我可担心死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有事 身体舒服不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打了一场壮烈的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够以和你许下约定的我醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说是一个奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我全都想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临死之前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在去往入学考试的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.18,0:17:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被卷入了电车事故
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生前希望成为医生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望救助他人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴望活着能够得到别人的感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱着这些想法 非常努力地用功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我临死前通过同意捐献把这具身躯留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我坚信 我这副身体应该救了某个需要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人肯定 一生都会感激素未相识的你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结弦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:18:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你已经没有遗憾了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果救了他人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我的人生也不至于那么糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不禁如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 我要消失了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有什么留恋的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么 想要一直和他们在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟他们是我的同伴啦 当然想在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我现在拥有另一种感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他们也和我一样感到心满意足
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起离开这个世界就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再开始一段新的人生也蛮不错的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你想让大家感受这种心境么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:18:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.37,0:18:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 我一见到你就被你用刀秒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你叫我证明你不会死嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和他们真是瞎折腾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且甭说她有多死脑筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真上课就会感到幸福么 参加社团活动就会感到满足么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为来到这个世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生前都没能好好地过青春时代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是这样的么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊 话说要怎么才能知道这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看在眼里还没察觉到么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得呀 这里原来是救济年轻人灵魂的场所啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时日向如果接住了那个二垒球的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许也会得偿所愿地消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和优衣真是太鸡婆了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:20:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩泽靠一己之力实现平生的夙愿 如愿以偿地消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何一人希望留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过在反抗人生的荒诞不经
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而奏希望告诉他们并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的人生并非荒诞不经
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴望让他们过上平凡的青春时光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来都在劝服打算在这个世界逗留的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是多么令人啼笑皆非
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是这么点小事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是双方为了贯彻自己的信念而互相对峙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至还造出武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都互相对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是太呆瓜了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是挺有自知之明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有你的话 也许能办到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是让我帮你么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来你应该已经消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你现在还留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能成为你第一个朋友么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所留恋的不正是这件事么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天为止我一直相信自己能做个很棒的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我想呵护的亲人都在30分钟之内被夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是太荒诞不经了么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种人生怎么能容忍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 正因如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为是想永远承受那种痛苦的她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才想救她于苦海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和这个糊涂天使 能做到么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不靠谱 果然不行么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这样的话他们还会继续对峙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.06,0:21:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.96,0:21:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我既是他们的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是奏的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的我不是正要做些什么么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.53,0:22:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你愿意协助我么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是该我来向你说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向天使说啥脑残话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.83,0:22:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解了 奏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家都从这里毕业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.14,0:22:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调换所有学科的答卷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企图陷害立华同学的团伙已经查出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.10,0:22:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于立华同学自己证明了笔迹不一致
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.30,0:22:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立华同学的清白得到了证明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.59,0:22:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新复职为我校学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.52,0:22:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进而作为代理会长的直井同学为副会长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊我靠 为啥我要落得如此下场
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.24,0:22:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把我们全部供出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.58,0:22:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些星间飞行到底意义何在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.61,0:22:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 咱俩少见地意见统一呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.78,0:23:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种心情只有飞过的人才了解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是星间飞行同志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.80,0:23:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 想要我脱衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱吧 脱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.90,0:23:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我停下 真烦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.60,0:23:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 真恶心 给我停下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.47,0:23:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要脱还是不脱？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说她貌似把这几天的事情全都忘了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.10,0:23:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.22,0:23:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是一百那方的人格胜利了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.37,0:23:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袭击我们的那边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.13,0:23:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一时间还以为能够友好相处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.90,0:23:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.42,0:23:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先必须要从他们那里打听出生前的往事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.29,0:23:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在目前这种失去敌人的状况下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.21,0:23:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要瞒着优莉行动是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.01,0:23:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说奏 我希望你能恢复学生会长的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.30,0:23:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能再和他们战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.95,0:23:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且 按照我的指示行动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.50,0:23:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这个作战计划很适合我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.73,0:24:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉又会让你独自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.05,0:24:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 等一切都结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.08,0:24:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束后……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.57,0:24:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时 到那时 我们会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.64,0:25:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回预告
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.56,0:25:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于你这个吉他手而糟蹋了整个乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.30,0:25:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使上…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.44,0:25:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是泛泛之辈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.08,0:25:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来她懂音乐呀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.89,0:25:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德式拱桥摔!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.16,0:25:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是其中一个梦想而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.85,0:25:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.07,0:25:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴治好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.13,0:25:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会是我们男人获得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.10,0:25:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这丫搞无间道么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.29,0:25:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KISS YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.92,0:25:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹般的射门!!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.96,0:25:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了!我来帮你实现
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.47,0:26:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的幸福…悉数剥夺了…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.52,0:26:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十章　Goodbye Days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,


